description:
The Seventh-day Adventist Church is a worldwide movement with over 21 million members in over 200 countries. As a global movement, what is our top priority? How are we fulfilling our mission to spread the Three Angels Messages, the gospel message of salvation, to every "nation, tribe, tongue, and people?" How are we reaching the youth, and, more importantly, how are we keeping them in the Church? ANN reports on this and more in todays exclusive report! 

Plus, dont miss even more inspiring mission reports from the South Pacific, South American, and Southern-Asia Pacific Division!

ANN Website: https://adventist.news/
ANN Twitter: https://twitter.com/adventistnews
